  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a dry skillet over medium heat.",
    "Warm the pandan leaf wrap in the skillet for 2 minutes on each side.",
    "Spread the goats cheese evenly over the center of the wrap, leaving a 1-inch border around the edges.",
    "Drizzle the floral honey over the cheese, then sprinkle with chopped almonds and lemon zest.",
    "Top with fresh mint leaves and a sprinkle of sesame seeds.",
    "Fold the bottom edge of the wrap up over the filling, then fold in the sides and roll the wrap into a tight cylinder.",
    "Heat the olive oil in the skillet over medium heat and cook the wrap for 2-3 minutes on each side, until crispy and golden.",
    "Sprinkle with garlic, salt, black pepper, and crushed red pepper before serving."
